headline: Moody’s Corporation Elects Lisa P. Sawicki to Board of Directors
summary: NEW YORK, January 12, 2026--Moody’s Corporation (NYSE:MCO) has elected Lisa P. Sawicki to the Company’s Board of Directors, effective March 16, 2026.

headline: Data center investments to hit $3 trillion over next five years, says Moody’s
summary: Investing.com -- At least $3 trillion will flow into data-center-related investments over the next five years, according to a report released by Moody’s Ratings on Monday.
